  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n\r\n*Summary*: several details are missed in current chat replies implementation (https://github.com/status-im/status-react/pull/6117)\r\n\r\nInitial design: zpl.io/a3l8dgY (Zeplin)\r\n\r\nScreenshot:\r\n![sample](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37297779/45289609-e8283c80-b4ed-11e8-8f7a-bfebf4075be3.png)\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n[comment]: # (Describe what you expected to happen.)\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n<img width=\"348\" alt=\"np_d\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/46671511-aa4a3100-cbdd-11e8-9b82-b515ac1c8f25.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Join any chat\r\n- Click on message to select it for reply\r\n\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\n\r\n*Summary*: \r\n\r\n- [ ] apply new design to close button\r\n- [ ] fix issues where last visible row is cut and there is no border in the top left corner (see screenshot in Actual behavior)\r\n- [ ] provide and implent design for long reply messages \r\n<img width=\"568\" alt=\"in_full\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/46671655-fbf2bb80-cbdd-11e8-986c-51add2acceec.png\">\r\n- [ ] fix issue where is no margins if user name is too long \r\n<img width=\"238\" alt=\"no_margin\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/46672296-b59e5c00-cbdf-11e8-9473-f6f201a67095.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n* Status version: nightly 09/10/2018\r\n* Operating System: Mac OSx\r\n",
