    "body": "Another issue to reply for the UI of desktop chat replies:\r\n\r\nType: **Bug**\r\n\r\nSummary: On desktop, when replying to a message of the user, in reply bubble in message input area, that icon is displayed as a square, not a circle.\r\nIt's especially visible when there's a profile icon set.\r\n\r\nReported separately from #6216 , since it's not an inconsistency with design.\r\nI could not find any design references for this on , https://www.figma.com/file/MRYBI5axcTwL4Ft8xAYhFOfy/Desktop?node-id=0%3A1 but it should be consistent with mobile.\r\n\r\n**Expected behaviour**\r\n\r\nThe icon displays as the circle (the same as in the chat) for mobile (iOS and Android)\r\n\r\n<img width=\"454\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/43638377/49455365-ba524b80-f7ef-11e8-9221-4c82b76cee76.png\">\r\n\r\n**Actual behaviour**\r\n\r\nThe icon displays as a square (original image used), and looks inconsistent\r\n\r\n<img width=\"678\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/43638377/49455397-cb02c180-f7ef-11e8-9bd9-9aaec91aa8dd.png\">\r\n\r\n<img width=\"676\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/43638377/49455424-d524c000-f7ef-11e8-93ab-c5dcecacef18.png\">\r\n\r\n**Reproduction:**\r\n\r\nOpen desktop app on device A\r\nStart 1-1 chat/join a public chat with a user who has a profile icon set\r\nClick on the message to quote it\r\n\n\n<blockquote><img src=\"/file/MRYBI5axcTwL4Ft8xAYhFOfy/thumbnail?ver=thumbnails/081fc3d9-2730-4ead-8fcb-484f0da270a0\" width=\"48\" align=\"right\"><div><img src=\"https://static.figma.com/app/icon/1/favicon.svg\" height=\"14\"> Figma</div><div><strong><a href=\"https://www.figma.com/file/MRYBI5axcTwL4Ft8xAYhFOfy/Desktop\">Figma</a></strong></div><div>Created with Figma</div></blockquote>",
